<div class="masthead-page">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
    <div class="panel-body application-overview">
      <div class="application-identity">
        <small>This is the application of</small>
        <h4>Applicant name</h4>
        <p>Today's date</p>
      </div>
      <div class="application-steps">
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <small>Basic information</small>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <small>Contact information</small>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <small>Schedule your interview</small>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <small>Submit your application</small>
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <div class="circle"></div>
            <small>Upload documentation</small>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="form-body">
	<section class="form-page basic-info">
		<div class="page-confirmation col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
			<section class="form-section">
				<h3>Congratulations!</h3>
				<p>Your application has been submitted.</p>
				<p>Someone from HSA will call you within 10 days for your phone interview.</p>
				<p>If you don't hear from them soon, please call them at XXX-XXX-XXXX, and say you need a phone interview to finalize your application.</p>
				<p>During your interview, you'll need information about:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Income</li>
					<li>Assets</li>
					<li>Expenses</li>
				</ul>
				<p>If you have documentation about your income, assets, expenses, you can upload them now.</p>
				<h4>Would you like a reminder about your interview? Check yes, and we will send you a text message reminder.</h4>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>
<div class="page-footer">
  <div class="footer-content col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
    <h3>Do you have any verification docs on hand?</h3>
    <a class="btn alternate-step" href="<%= url('/first_id_doc') %>">
   	<h5>Yes, I have docs to uplaod</h5></a>
   	<h5 class="or">or</h5>
    <a class="btn next-step" href="<%= url('/application/basic_info') %>">
   	<h5>No, I'm done for today.</h5></a>
  </div>
</div>